    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, you won\u2019t find another one like this\u2014it\u2019s in stunning, showroom-ready shape and has been totally babied since day one. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person! I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in the garage and followed every service to a T. I'm really sad to see it go, but I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
