    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 in pristine condition. This example features the S54 3.2L inline-six, a masterpiece of engineering with individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative: the dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled for optimal cam phasing, and the rear subframe\u2014a known point of fatigue\u2014has been preemptively reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. Power is managed via a precise Getrag six-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, providing linear torque delivery and exceptional corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its original telepathic feedback thanks to fresh bushings and a perfectly calibrated suspension setup. This is a turn-key, mechanically synchronous machine for the purist collector.",
      "price": 46500.0,
