    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a rare find for the discerning collector: a truly showroom-quality vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This meticulously maintained gem has been kept in a climate-controlled garage since day one, shielded from the elements and preserved in a state of absolute perfection. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero chips, swirls, or imperfections, while the factory wheels remain entirely free of curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury, featuring supple, untouched leather seating that still retains its original factory scent. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the responsive infotainment display, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive, documented service history from the original dealership. With exceptionally low mileage and a clean, single-owner history, this is more than just a used car; it is a time capsule. If you demand the absolute best without compromise, your search ends here.",
