      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have got to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014not a single scratch or smudge in sight. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh car feel. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect and ready for its next big adventure, this is the one. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it!",
